    Combine json pieces

    Source: R/combine.R
    combine.Rd

    Combine json pieces

    Usage

    combine(x)

    Arguments

    x

    Input, of class json

    Examples

    x <- '{"foo": 5, "bar": 7}' %>% select(a = .foo)
combine(x)
#> {
#>     "foo": 5,
#>     "bar": 7
#> }
